Class WallNut

java.lang.Object
domain.Character
domain.Plant
domain.Defensive
domain.WallNut
public class WallNut extends Defensive
WallNut is a defensive plant in the game with high durability. It is utilized to absorb damage from incoming threats, protecting other plants. As an extension of the Defensive class, WallNut inherits features to enhance its survivability.
